Saffron Barker Imagine unironically recreating "The Dice Man". That's a colossal yikes from me.

It's likely that you didn't know about that troubling book before you made this video, but please do some research into your subject matter before presenting ideas that can take a dark turn very quickly.

Especially with how "extreme" our generation can be about things(see: dangerous challenges, party games that end in manslaughter, "fun trends" that get people killed).

I really wouldn't like to see what our generation would do with that kind of mindset if it had a resurgence, that one book did enough damage as is.

I saw this on the trending page and that alone has my anxiety spiking, I really hope this doesn't catch on.
